《'''圣战'''》（{{lang-en|''Jihad''}}）是[[美国|美国]][[敲击金属|敲击金属]]乐队[[超级杀手合唱团|超级杀手合唱团]]的一首歌曲，收录在其2006年的[[音乐专辑|音乐专辑]]《基督幻觉》（{{lang|en|''Christ Illusion''}}）中。这首歌想像并描绘了一名参与[[九一一袭击事件|九一一袭击事件]]恐怖分子的观点，再以[[穆罕默德·阿塔|穆罕默德·阿塔]]所留遗书中的内容作为口语歌词结束，[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]认定阿塔是驾驭第一架飞机撞上[[世界贸易中心|世界贸易中心]]的“自杀式恐怖分子头目”。《圣战》由吉他手杰夫·汉尼曼主创，歌词则是由汉尼曼和歌手汤姆·阿拉亚共同创作。

这首歌曲在乐评人中所获评价褒贬不一，评论大多围绕歌词中的争议性议题展开。还有评论将《圣战》和“超级杀手合唱团”1986年同样由汉尼曼创作的歌曲《[[死亡天使_(歌曲)|死亡天使]]》相比较，这首歌发布时同样激起了很大的争议。

[[孟买|孟买]]基督教团体“天主教世俗论坛”的约瑟夫·迪亚斯（{{lang|en|Joseph Dias}}）针对《圣战》的歌词表达了担忧，还成功促使{{lang|en|[[EMI|EMI]]}}印度公司召回了专辑《基督幻觉》，该公司也没有计划在印度重新发行这张专辑。{{lang|en|[[美国广播公司|ABC-TV]]}}广播标准和实践部在超级杀手合唱团通过《[[吉米·坎摩尔直播秀|吉米·坎摩尔直播秀]]》首度现身美国电视网络时审查了这首歌，只有在开场时显示了节目的主创人员名单，歌词的40%都被略去。

== 源起 ==
[[File:Mohamed_Atta.jpg|thumb]]留下了一封有关2001年9月11日袭击“动机”的信件。《圣战》的高潮部分就采用了信中的部分语句，以说唱台词形式表演<ref name="KingAtkinson">{{cite web | title = Songs About God and Satan - Part 1: An Interview With Slayer's Kerry King | author = Atkinson, Peter | publisher = KNAC.com | date = 2006-05-24 | url = http://knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=4550 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140725084516/http://knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=4550 | archivedate = 2014-07-25 }}</ref>]]
《圣战》由吉他手杰夫·汉尼曼主创，歌手汤姆·阿拉亚则共同创作了歌词<ref name="AlbumNotes">''Christ Illusion'' album notes, 2006-08-08. American Recordings, 9362-44300-2</ref>。两人之前都曾为超级杀手合唱团的歌曲创作过争议性的歌词，其中汉尼曼曾创作过包括《死亡天使》（{{lang|en|''Angel of Death''}}）和《{{lang|en|SS-3}}》在内的争议性歌曲，通过这些歌曲探讨[[奥斯维辛集中营|奥斯维辛集中营]]医生[[约瑟夫·门格勒|约瑟夫·门格勒]]和[[第三帝国|第三帝国]]亲信[[莱因哈德·海德里希|莱因哈德·海德里希]]之类纳粹人物的暴行；阿拉亚则在歌曲《{{lang|en|213}}》和《死皮面具》（{{lang|en|''Dead Skin Mask''}}）中分别深入研究了连环杀人犯[[杰弗里·达默|杰弗里·达默]]（{{lang|en|Jeffrey Dahmer}}）和[[艾德·盖恩|艾德·盖恩]]的生活。《圣战》是以911事件恐怖分子的视角出发，设想了这些“敌人”可能会有的想法<ref name="KingAtkinson" /><ref name="SunInterview">{{cite web | title = It's carry on thrashing' | author =  | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | publisher = The Sun Online | date =  | url = http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/sftw/article60093.ece | archive-date = 2016-03-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310063916/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/sftw/article60093.ece | dead-url = no }}</ref>。歌曲高潮部分采用了[[穆罕默德·阿塔|穆罕默德·阿塔]]留下的一封有关2001年9月11日袭击“动机”的信件，以说唱台词形式表演<ref name="KingAtkinson" />。[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]认为阿塔正是[[九一一袭击事件|九一一袭击事件]]中的“自杀式恐怖分子头目”，他劫持并控制了第一架撞上[[世界贸易中心|世界贸易中心]]的[[美国航空11号班机恐怖袭击|美国航空11号班机]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Ross | first = Brian | title = FBI Informant Says Agents Missed Chance to Stop 9/11 Ringleader Mohammed Atta | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | newspaper = ABC News | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/Whistleblowers/911-ringleader-mohammed-atta-stopped-fbi-informant/story?id=8540605 | date = 2009-09-10 | archivedate = 2013-12-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131230234554/http://abcnews.go.com/Blotter/Whistleblowers/911-ringleader-mohammed-atta-stopped-fbi-informant/story?id=8540605 }}</ref>。

吉他手[[克里·金|克里·金]]（{{lang|en|Kerry King}}）一直直言不讳地为《圣战》辩护，声称这首歌拥有《基督幻觉》中“最酷的视角”<ref name="KingAtkinson" />。“这些新歌根本没有什么政治主题，”金在接受采访时称：“《圣战》、《{{lang|en|[[Eyes_of_the_Insane|Eyes of the Insane]]}}》——这都（不过）是电视里向我们喷涌而出的内容”<ref>{{cite news | title = After 25 years, Slayer keeps casting metal | author = Beck, Aaron | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | publisher = The Columbus Dispatch | date = 2007-02-10 | via = HighBeam Research | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-159132902.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140921122337/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-159132902.html | archive-date = 2014-09-21 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。他还进一步指出，虽然有些人认为如此，但超级杀手合唱团无意宣传恐怖分子的战争视角和意识形态理念<ref name="KingAtkinson" />。他们无意在“这个星球上的其他任何乐队都已经拥有的某种特定视角”议题上纠结，所以自己必须要代表某种不同的观点<ref name="KingAtkinson" />。在金看来，“我们是杀手，所以我们必须与众不同”<ref name="KingAtkinson" />。

美国[[唱作人|唱作人]][[史蒂夫·厄尔|史蒂夫·厄尔]]（{{lang|en|Steve Earle}}）在创作2002年专辑《耶路撒冷》（{{lang|en|''Jerusalem''}}）中的歌曲《约翰·沃克的蓝调》（{{lang|en|''John Walker's Blues''}}）时尝试类似的概念，采用[[阿富汗战争_(2001年)|2001年阿富汗战争]]期间被[[驻伊美军|驻伊美军]]俘虏的[[塔利班|塔利班]]恐怖分子[[约翰·沃克·林德|约翰·沃克·林德]]的视角，林德出生于[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]，是一位美国公民<ref name="KingAtkinson" /><ref name="Sculley">{{cite web | title = Metal gods Slayer gear up for this summer's most brutal road trek, the Unholy Alliance Tour | author = Sculley, Alan | publisher = CityBeat.com | date =  | url = http://www.citybeat.com/2006-06-14/music.shtml | accessdate = 2008-07-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080706074505/http://citybeat.com/2006-06-14/music.shtml | archivedate = 2008-07-06 }}</ref>。厄尔因这首曲目受到了批评，金认为《圣战》也会遭遇同样的反应<ref name="KingAtkinson" /><ref name="Sculley" />：“人们在看过歌词前就已经有了先入为主的成见。这不但是人的本性，而且也可以说是美国的本性”<ref name="Sculley" />。

== 曲式结构 ==
《圣战》长3分31秒<ref name="AllMusicReview">{{cite web | title = Allmusic Review - ''Christ Illusion'' | author = Jurek, Thom | publisher = [[Allmusic|Allmusic]] | url = http://www.allmusic.com/album/christ-illusion-mw0000572727 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140629072208/http://www.allmusic.com/album/christ-illusion-mw0000572727 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2014-06-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，以快速而[[固定低音|简短]]的音符开始，伴随着[[爵士鼓|鼓手]][[戴夫·隆巴多|戴夫·隆巴多]]（{{lang|en|Dave Lombardo}}）轻踏踩镲<ref name="AllMusicReview" />。各种音符的节奏平衡地混合起来，乐曲速度很快但又摇摆不定<ref name="NYTReview">{{cite news | last = Ratliff | first = Ben | title = New CD's | work = The New York Times | pages = | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 2006-08-14 | url = | accessdate =}}</ref>，同时吉他反复演奏出[[固定低音|连复段]]<ref name="Popmatters">{{cite web | title = Christ Illusion - Review | author = Begrand, Adrien | publisher = Popmatters | date =  | url = http://www.popmatters.com/review/slayer-christ-illusion/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131122175123/http://www.popmatters.com/review/slayer-christ-illusion/ | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2013-11-22 }}</ref>，旋律与乐队1986年的歌曲《死亡天使》有类似之处<ref name="Stylus">{{cite web |title=Christ Illusion - Review |author=Lee, Cosmo |publisher=Stylus Magazine |date= |url=http://stylusmagazine.com/reviews/slayer/christ-illusion.htm |accessdate=2014-08-14 |archivedate=2014-03-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330024122/http://stylusmagazine.com/reviews/slayer/christ-illusion.htm |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。接下来吉他的短小旋律速度减慢，再在隆巴多强烈的第五号鼓声两段式支撑下向前爆发<ref name="NYTReview" />。

{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}网站评论员认为，与《基督幻觉》中的其它曲目相比，《圣战》的乐式结构不值一提：《圣战》、《血肉风暴》（{{lang|en|''Flesh Storm''}}）、《骨架基督》（{{lang|en|''Skeleton Christ''}}）《{{lang|en|Supremist}}》中的连复段、调音、[[速度_(音乐)|节奏]]和[[改编_(音乐)|编排]]都存在太多的相似之处<ref name="IGN">{{cite web | title = Christ Illusion - Review | author = Patrizio, Andy | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140814051508/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/08/14/slayer-christ-illusion | publisher = IGN | date = 2006-08-14 | url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2006/08/14/slayer-christ-illusion | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-14 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|MusicOMH.com}}网站的伊恩·罗宾逊（{{lang|en|Ian Robinson}}）也持负面看法，认为歌曲中所采用的那些超级杀手合唱团的技巧已经略显过时，虽然还是很有气氛，但其独奏部分的样板式演出已经有些过头了<ref name="MusicOMH">{{cite web | title = Christ Illusion - Review | author = Robinson, Ian | publisher = MusicOMH.com | date = 2006-08-21 | url = http://www.musicomh.com/reviews/albums/slayer-christ-illusion | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130709003735/http://www.musicomh.com/reviews/albums/slayer-christ-illusion | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-07-09 }}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
2006年6月26日，《圣战》和《基督幻觉》中另外两首歌曲《{{lang|en|Eyes of the Insane}}》和《邪教》（{{lang|en|''Cult''}}）开始通过西班牙语网站{{lang|en|Rafabasa.com}}发布流媒体<ref>{{cite web | title = SLAYER: Three New Tracks Available In Streaming Audio | author =  | publisher = Blabbermouth.net | date = 2006-06-26 | archivedate = 2013-07-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130709003735/http://www.musicomh.com/reviews/albums/slayer-christ-illusion | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.roadrunnerrecords.com/blabbermouth.net/news.aspx?mode=Article&newsitemID=54247 | accessdate = 2013-07-09 }}</ref>。《基督幻觉》是超级杀手合唱团的第9张[[音乐专辑|录音室唱片]]，于2006年8月8日发行<ref name="AllMusicReview" />，其中《圣战》一曲所获评价褒贬不一。

{{lang|en|Blabbermouth}}网站的唐·凯伊（{{lang|en|Don Kaye}}）认为，《基督幻觉》中“屈指可数的几首歌曲”“要么太过一般，要么就是在编排上过于拙劣，难以达到良好的效果”，他还特别点名批评了其中两首曲目：“我说的就是你，《圣战》和《骨架基督》”<ref name="BlabbermouthReview">{{cite web | title = Blabbermouth Review - ''Christ Illusion'' | author = Kaye, Don | publisher = Blabbermouth.net | url = http://www.blabbermouth.net/cdreviews/christ-illusion/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140814054057/http://www.blabbermouth.net/cdreviews/christ-illusion/ | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2014-08-14 }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的本·拉特利夫（{{lang|en|Ben Ratliff}}）认为，这首歌的内容“可以预见会很强硬，但让我们来做个对比。与[[马丁·艾米斯|马丁·艾米斯]]（{{lang|en|Martin Amis}}）近期的短篇故事《穆罕默德·阿塔最后的日子》（{{lang|en|''The Last Days of Muhammad Atta''}}）相比，这首歌多了一层强硬，少了一分理性。（但要是）和[[基地组织|基地组织]]录像带中的信息相比，这强硬又有不及了”<ref name="NYTReview" />。{{lang|en|KNAC.com}}网站的彼得·阿特金森（{{lang|en|Peter Atkinson}}）对歌曲同样没有好感，他在评论中这样写道：<ref name="KNACReview">{{cite web | title = KNAC Review - Christ Illusion | author = Atkinson, Peter | publisher = KNAC.com | date = 2006-07-24 | archivedate = 2014-07-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140729140420/http://www.knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=4789 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=4789 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 }}</ref>

{{cquote|……汉尼曼和阿拉亚在过去一些“困难”主题中也曾采用过同类型的战术：就事论事、超脱于字里行间之外。无论是《死亡天使》中约瑟夫·门格勒的纳粹暴行，还是《213》和《死皮面具》中杰弗里·达默与艾德·盖恩的残忍癖好都有着非常好的效果。但在这里感觉却不大对味，似乎纯粹只是为了激起人们的情绪……但超级杀手合唱团通常能做得远比这样要好。}}

不过也并非所有的评价都属负面。{{lang|en|[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]}}网站的汤姆·尤雷克（{{lang|en|Thom Jurek}}）就称赞乐队在节奏上的创新，对四四拍做出了最疯狂的解构<ref name="AllMusicReview" />。《奥斯汀纪事报》（{{lang|en|''Austin Chronicle''}}）的马克·萨夫洛夫（{{lang|en|Marc Savlov}}）要求读者去感受其中的阴森和恐怖，无需在意疯狂的节奏，称“阿拉亚对表现一位自杀式炸弹袭击者的尝试实在太有说服力了”<ref>{{cite web |title=Christ Illusion - Review |author=Savlov, Marc |publisher=Austin Chronicle |date=2006-09-01 |archivedate=2007-09-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930184555/http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Issue/review?oid=oid%3A399559 |url=http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Issue/review?oid=oid:399559 |accessdate=2007-09-30 }}</ref>。

克里·金本期望由《圣战》提名[[第49届格莱美奖|第49届格莱美奖]][[格莱美奖最佳金属表演|最佳金属表演奖]]，他认为实际获得提名的《{{lang|en|Eyes of the Insane}}》是合唱团第9张录音室唱片《基督幻觉》中“表现最不理想”的歌曲<ref>{{cite news | last = Piccoli | first = Sean | title = Grammy for Slayer's 11th album shows metal legends are now a household name | work = | pages = | publisher = Sun-Sentinel.com | date = 2007-02-21 | url = | accessdate =}}</ref>。虽然金抱持着这样的看法，但《{{lang|en|Eyes of the Insane}}》还是为超级杀手合唱团赢得了他们的第一座[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]<ref>{{cite web | title = SLAYER Wins GRAMMY In 'Best Metal Performance' Category | author =  | publisher = Blabbermouth.net | date = 2007-02-11 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | url = http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-wins-grammy-in-best-metal-performance-category/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131222143657/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-wins-grammy-in-best-metal-performance-category/ | archivedate = 2013-12-22 }}</ref>。金还表示：“我喜欢演奏《圣战》，因为我可以变着法子演奏吉他，杰夫会在让乐曲的开场比较安静，这样你就能听见歌迷们对这首歌的疯狂表现，通常来说，歌迷并不见得会在一首歌的开头就有这样的表现”<ref>{{cite web | title = Slayer Interview Pt II | author = Gamble, Billy | publisher = Rocknworld.com | date =  | url = http://www.rocknworld.com/features/07/slayer2.shtml | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2014-07-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140706064713/http://www.rocknworld.com/features/07/slayer2.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 争议 ===
{{listen|filename=Slayer Jihad.ogg
|title=《圣战》（2006年）
|description=《圣战》以快速而简短的吉他连复段开始<ref name="Popmatters" />，旋律与乐队1986年的歌曲《[[死亡天使_(歌曲)|死亡天使]]》有类似之处<ref name="Stylus" />。}}

《圣战》的歌词内容引起了多个领域的争议。{{lang|en|KNAC.com}}网站的彼得·阿特金森就指出，这首歌“无疑会成为《基督幻觉》中最具争议性的曲目。”2005年6月，[[世界娱乐新闻网|世界娱乐新闻网]]宣布，歌曲遭到泄露的歌词内容已经激怒了[[九一一袭击事件|9/11]]遇难者的亲属。<ref>{{cite web | title = SLAYER Spark 9/11 Controversy | publisher = Blabbermouth.net | date = 2006-05-27 | url = http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-spark-9-11-controversy/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140814073717/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-spark-9-11-controversy/ | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2014-08-14 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

[[孟买|孟买]]基督教团体“天主教世俗论坛”的约瑟夫·迪亚斯向所在地区的警察专员发出了一份备忘录，表示担心《圣战》会冒犯“敏感的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]……和尊重所有信仰的世俗印度人”<ref name="IllusionRecalled">{{cite web | title = SLAYER's 'Christ Illusion' Album Recalled Following Christian Group Protests | author =  | publisher = Blabbermouth.net | date = 2006-10-06 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2013-12-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-s-christ-illusion-album-recalled-following-christian-group-protests/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131222140811/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-s-christ-illusion-album-recalled-following-christian-group-protests/ }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[EMI|EMI]]}}印度与天主教世俗论坛举行会面，对发行这张唱片表示道歉，还召回了所有副本，并且没有重新发行的计划<ref name="IllusionRecalled" />。2006年10月11日，该公司宣布所有库存副本都已销毁<ref name="Offensive' album pulled in India">{{cite web | title = 'Offensive' album pulled in India | author =  | publisher = [[英国广播公司新闻网|BBC New Online]] | date = 2006-10-11 | archivedate = 2013-12-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131216032551/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6039976.stm | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6039976.stm | accessdate = 2014-08-14 }}</ref>。《圣战》和拉里·卡罗尔（{{lang|en|Larry Carroll}}）为专辑绘制的争议性封面以及歌曲中挑衅性质的歌词，都是{{lang|en|EMI}}印度公司做此决定的具体原因<ref name="IllusionRecalled" />。阿拉亚之前预料，考虑到911事件的影响，《圣战》会在美国引起强烈反弹<ref name="SunInterview" />，但实际上并非如此。他认为这部分是因为人们会把这首歌曲视为不过是“超级杀手的本色表现”<ref name="Luxi">{{cite web | title = SLAYER - Jeff Hanneman | author = Lahtinen, Luxi | publisher = Metal-rules.com | date = 2006-12-18 | archivedate = 2013-12-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131220132212/http://www.metal-rules.com/zine/index.php?option=content&task=view&id=737&Itemid=60 | url = http://www.metal-rules.com/zine/index.php?option=content&task=view&id=737&Itemid=60 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | df =  }}</ref>。汉尼曼预料，穆斯林群体要么会因《圣战》“拥抱”超级杀手合唱团，要么就会憎恨他们，911事件的受害者及亲属也会就这首歌的主题批评乐队<ref name="HannemanSteffens">{{cite web | title = Gnarly Charlie's exclusive interview with Slayer Guitarist Jeff Hanneman | author = Steffens, Charlie | publisher = KNAC.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140724104222/http://knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=4653 | deadurl = no | date = 2006-05-30 | url = http://www.knac.com/article.asp?ArticleID=4653 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2014-07-24 }}</ref>。

2007年1月19日，超级杀手合唱团走上了{{lang|en|[[美国广播公司|ABC-TV]]}}的《[[吉米·坎摩尔直播秀|吉米·坎摩尔直播秀]]》，这也是乐团首次在美国电视网络亮相。乐队一共表演了6首歌曲，但《圣战》实际只播出了最开头的一分钟内容<ref>{{cite web | title = SLAYER On 'Jimmy Kimmel Live!': 'Eyes Of The Insane' Performance Posted Online | author =  | publisher = Blabbermouth.net | date = 2007-01-20 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2013-12-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131222140757/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-on-jimmy-kimmel-live-eyes-of-the-insane-performance-posted-online/ | url = http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-on-jimmy-kimmel-live-eyes-of-the-insane-performance-posted-online/ }}</ref>。电视台的广播标准和实践部[[审查制度|审查]]了《圣战》，而且在节目播出前仅一天时告知超级杀手合唱团，有约40%的歌词内容遭到了了删除<ref name="KansasCityStarBlabber">{{cite web | title = SLAYER Guitarist Says ABC-TV Put Last-Minute 'Gag Order' On Band's 'Jimmy Kimmel' Performance | author =  | publisher = Blabbermouth.net | date = 2007-02-03 | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | archivedate = 2014-08-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140814091815/http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-guitarist-says-abc-tv-put-last-minute-gag-order-on-band-s-jimmy-kimmel-performance/ | url = http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/slayer-guitarist-says-abc-tv-put-last-minute-gag-order-on-band-s-jimmy-kimmel-performance/ }}</ref>。克里·金此后证实，当时乐队很想退出演出，但最终还是决定“由他去吧”<ref name="KansasCityStarBlabber" />。

